色，以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/future">未来</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/young-thug">年轻的Thug</a>为特色。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-celebrates-winning-super-bowl-bet-on-kansas-city-chiefs-i-won-a-million-dollars-3586173">德雷克邮报庆祝堪萨斯城酋长赢得超级碗的赌注：“我赢得了一百万美元”</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现。</p> ;
